                    "description": "# Diyetisyen Detayını Getir\n\n## Genel Bakış\nBelirli bir UUID'ye sahip diyetisyenin profil bilgilerini getirir.\n\n## HTTP Method & Path\n`GET /exapi/dietitians/{id}`\n\n## Yetkilendirme\nBearer token gereklidir\n\n## Path Parameters\n- **id** (UUID, required): Diyetisyen UUID'si\n\n## Response\n\n### Başarılı (200)\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"660e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001\",\n  \"firstName\": \"Ayşe\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Kaya\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Ayşe Kaya\",\n  \"bio\": \"10 yıllık deneyimli diyetisyen\",\n  \"specialization\": \"Sporcu Beslenmesi\",\n  \"experienceYear\": 10,\n  \"city\": \"İstanbul\",\n  \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-15T09:00:00\"\n}\n```\n\n## Örnek Request\n```bash\ncurl -X GET http://localhost:8080/exapi/dietitians/660e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001 \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer {token}\"\n```"
